HEADWORD: Fructuous
<hw>Fruc"tu*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>fructuosus</ets>: cf, F. <ets>fructueux</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Fruitful; productive; profitable.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Nothing <qex>fructuous</qex> or profitable.</q>
